Joan Alexander https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joan_Alexander 0 Joan Alexander (born Louise Abrass; April 16, 1915 – May 21, 2009) was an American actress known for her role as Lois Lane on the radio serial The Adventures of Superman and the animated films the Fleischer Superman cartoons.
